5. Game:mah-jongg == House:townhouse
6. Cigar:pall-mall == Job:firefighter
7. Game:backgammon == Cigar:dunhill
8. House:palace is in the middle
9. Sport:weightlifting is on the far left
10. Cigar:blend is on the left or right of Job:mechanic
11. Job:accountants is on the left or right of Cigar:dunhill
12. Cigar:pokermaster == House:craftsman
13. Sport:climbing == Cigar:prince
14. Sport:weightlifting is on the left or right of Game:poker
15. Cigar:blend is on the left or right of House:art-deco

